            <h3 class="title dark-indigo advantages">The problem</h3>
            <p class="advantages-text steel">With the stakes that come with the line of business of Capptions’ clients, immutability is a crucial characteristic for enterprises. A small error may cause mayhem for global operations at places like airports, oil-terminals and factories. The existing possibility of manipulating these (inspection) reports may cause immense damages.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns advantages">
        <div class="column advantages image left-side">
          <div class="advantages left-side column-subdiv">
            <img src="/assets/rocks/rock-2.svg" class="rock-rocket">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-3" src="/assets/small-rock-3.svg">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-4" src="/assets/small-rock-4.svg">
