          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Compliance used to be a set of rules on a static paper, which don’t allow automation.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Data immutability</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Inspection reports become immutable through hashing and anchoring them on LTO.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">(Inspection) reports are prone to a mutation in case of catastrophic failure</td>
        </tr>


        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Costs / Speed of anchoring</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
